ady to join the Japanese side to actively implement the consensus reached between the two sides. Continue to close high-level exchanges. ASEM summit, the leaders&#39; meeting of China, Japan and Korea, the APEC Economic Leaders Meeting and the East Asia Series Summit held within this year, the two leaders met in the multilateral occasions, in a timely manner on Sino-Japanese relations and the common concern strengthen communication. During the year, held the second meeting of high-level economic dialogue mechanism, in-depth exchanges between the two countries on macroeconomic policy, especially substantive progress in energy conservation and environmental protection cooperation to promote economic and trade cooperation between the two countries. Third, vigorously promote cultural exchanges. This year is the 30th anniversary of the Sino-Japanese Peace and Friendship Treaty, the Japan Youth Friendly Exchange Year. The two sides should vigorously carry out personnel and cultural exchanges between the two peoples, especially the young, the mutual understanding and friendship. Fourth, strengthen defense exchanges continue to enhance the security and mutual trust. <br> Yasuo Fukuda agreed with Hu on the development of Japan-China relations. He said that in recent years, the Sino-Japanese strategic and mutually beneficial relations have made important progress. I hope the two sides will continue to strengthen political dialogue, expand personnel and cultural exchanges, and continue to carry out the field of defense exchanges. (Lsjt.net) <br> Yasuo Fukuda said will attend the opening ceremony of the Beijing Olympic Games the (history TodayOnHistory.com) and wished the Beijing Olympic Games a great success. <br> Hu said the Beijing Olympic Games organized by the Japanese government, (TodayinHistory.cn) Japanese Olympic Committee, Japan supported the sincere care and support of the Parliamentary Union of the Beijing Olympics and the friendly people from all walks of life. We 